"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:18:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17875a124bec733368c7d5a7aeb985d3648a7e26","tid":1583834,"uid":80936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ce267882bff437bfc06969396a93ca4303a71ac","tid":1583834,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:11:29.000Z","msg":"三毛又想散播fake news主意"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T07:29:27.000Z","msg":"啱啊<br />\nfake news啊<br />\n班狗撳得住啲證據<br />\n就代表冇發生<br />\n你有冇睇爆眼女義士個post？<br />\n知唔知佢屋企人俾班狗做咗啲乜？<br />\n<br />\n爆眼都咁樣<br />\n更何況強姦同埋死人？<br />\n<br />\n根本你個心態就係當班受害者係condom<br />\n只要唔係發生係你身上<br />\n咁就唔緊要啦<br />\n只要當事人冇出黎<br />\n就當冇事發生啦<br />\n<br />\n成日話冇fact check就係fake news<br />\ndllm你唔用輿論壓力迫班狗出黎講<br />\n又有邊個fact check到呢幾單嘢？<br />\n<br />\n而家你哋係到幫班狗<br />\n去達成佢哋嘅目的啊<br />\n<br />\n你話我三毛<br />\n你鐘意就講啦<br />\n<br />\n冇行動post 根本就唔關fake news事<br />\n有邊個上連登<br />\n會淨係睇一個post就off<br />\n更何況係唔係fake news<br />\n你都未證實到<br />\n<br />\n反正你哋都只係當人哋係condom<br />\n你哋永遠唔會明白當事人有幾絕望<br />\n為咗生存<br />\n喺度避東避西<br />\n連自己嘅公義都爭取唔到<br />\n<br />\n然而你哋就喺度講話佢地單嘢係fake news<br />\n<br />\n好，講fact check咗嘅<br />\n新屋嶺嘅傷者已經被證實咗<br />\n咁你哋又做咗啲咩？<br />\n<br />\n連美國記者為佢地所做嘅嘢<br />\n都多過你班仆街"},{"pid":"2da1d0343ebd60df49ff6bceda215896ee319e38","tid":1583834,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T07:30:15.000Z","msg":"有野想捐可以FB搵我地香港自由之書阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[澄清]國難五金課金問題&mdash;照舊課！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n國難五金專訪<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521301/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521301/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nFB: 國難五金, 香港自由之書"}]}